e: ￹`Ma~`pacekil~ `no~ `Fangcalay~ `'Adingo~ `kako~.￺I am inspired by the Holy Spirit.￻我被聖靈感動
￹`Ma~`cekil~ `ko~ `cikawasay~.￺The medium is aroused by possession by a spirit.￻巫師被精靈激發
￹`Ma~`cekil~ `ko~ `wawa~.￺The child is suddenly awakened and so cries.￻小孩突然被驚嚇而哭起來
d.f: ￹￺to take off guard * to suddenly be moved upon￻突然受驚或被感動
